item.title: Traveling to Bournemouth
item.description: I arrived in Bournemouth (England) with cold and snow, my first Erasmus trip, start making contacts (networking) on a place where web developers are very welcome, some beautiful places to visit, some small PHP conferences (@PHPDorset) but all in there was lovely, a young town center full of students. In the time that I was there, 3 months, I was finding places to visit so, no time to focus on business plans (future plans).
